{
  "name": "ClickIn360 Onboarding A — Kickoff",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Self-hosted n8n Community Edition\n\n**No Settings → Variables** on the free plan. Edit the **Config: Edit These Values** Set node (yellow fields) in each workflow instead.\n\nOptional: you can also set OS/Docker env vars on the n8n container — not required if you use the Config node.\n\n**Triggers:** quote.accepted, invoice.paid, onboarding.manual_start\n\nEdit Config: `crm_base_url` (e.g. https://www.clickin360.com).\n\nKickoff email uses public `/es/book-call` or `/en/book-call` — not `/api/leads/booking-offers` (staff API only).",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ],
      "id": "72e73bee-4677-45c3-b0d0-a1a63e07a222",
